ARCH: 0.4
CONT: stanza
PATH: broker/src/stanza
DEP:
DESC: XML stanza parser — extracts routing headers (from, to, type, mentions), preserves raw XML for forwarding

MOD: parser
  FILES: mod.rs; parser.rs
  OWN: parse; parse_message; parse_presence; ParseError
  BND: Attribute extraction only — body content is opaque, never parsed or modified

MOD: types
  FILE: types.rs
  OWN: Stanza; MessageStanza; PresenceStanza; MessageType; PresenceStatus; Destination; ResolvedMention; resolve_destination; resolve_agent_name; enrich_from; enrich_to_for_remote
  BND: Pure types and routing functions — no I/O, no state, no side effects
